<paragraph blockId="0.[1266,2150,596,1229]" pageId="0" pageNumber="107">• Small to medium-sized lagomorphs with short fluffy tails, soft thick pelage, and large eyes; ears project upward; hindlimbs longer than forelimbs.</paragraph>
